Tragedy struck on Wednesday at the ancient town of Arigidi Akoko North West Local Government Area of Ondo State when a 40-year-old mother, Bello Aina killed her 4-year-old daughter, Sadia Bello. The woman who lives at Ayase Quarters, said she killed the child due to the inability of the deceased daughter to walk after spending fortunes in various spiritual home without healing. According to police sources, the suspect confessed that she was the only person spending money on the deceases since she didnâ€™t have husband to assist her. Confirming the development, the Divisional Police Officer, Okeagbe Division, Ibitayo Adetanrni, a Superintendent of Police said the case had been transferred to Akure for further investigation. 